                <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Works with Any LINQ Provider</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">
                    Use Linqraft with EF Core or any other LINQ provider that supports
                    <InlineCode>IQueryable</InlineCode> / <InlineCode>IEnumerable</InlineCode>.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-xl border border border-gray-800 bg-gray-900 p-5">
